WEBVTT

00:01:26.763 --> 00:01:30.563
and in a moment someone
will transform and tear you all apart

00:01:30.563 --> 00:01:32.903
unless you can cure them first.

00:01:32.903 --> 00:01:35.953
How can you divide the antidote 
into perfect fifths,

00:01:35.953 --> 00:01:39.483
cure the secret werewolf, 
and save everyone?

00:01:39.483 --> 00:01:43.673
Pause the video now if you want
to figure it out for yourself.

00:01:43.673 --> 00:01:44.843
Answer in 3

00:01:44.843 --> 00:01:45.963
Answer in 2

00:01:45.963 --> 00:01:47.913
Answer in 1

00:01:47.913 --> 00:01:51.083
When it comes to puzzles that
involve cutting and rearranging,

00:01:51.083 --> 00:01:54.043
it’s often helpful to actually 
take a piece of paper

00:01:54.043 --> 00:01:56.883
and try cutting it up to see what
you can get.

00:01:56.883 --> 00:02:02.033
If we cut BF and DH we’d get fourths,
but we need fifths.